<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٢٠:</span> مَا شُرُوطُ الصَّلَاةِ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>شُرُوطُ الصَّلَاةِ تِسْعَةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - الْإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ - الْعَقْلُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣ - التَّمْييزُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٤ - رَفْعُ الْحَدَثِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٥ - إِزَالَةُ النَّجَاسَةِ مِنَ الْبَدَنِ وَالثَّوْبِ وَالْبُقْعَةِ <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٦ - سَتْرُ الْعَوْرَةِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٧ - دُخُولُ الْوَقْتِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٨ - اسْتِقْبَالُ الْقِبْلَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٩ - النِّيَّةُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>* * *<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٢١:</span> مَا أَرْكَانُ الصَّلَاةِ؟<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أَرْكَانُ الصَّلَاةِ أَرْبَعَةَ عَشَرَ رُكْنًا،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ عَلَى النَّحْوِ التَّالِي:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١ - الْقِيَامُ مَعَ الْقُدْرَةِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) البُقْعَةُ: هِيَ مَكَانُ الصَّلاةِ وَمَوضِعُ السُّجُودِ.</p> </div>